161
00:07:39,603 --> 00:07:40,762
in a coma.

162
00:07:45,123 --> 00:07:45,723
Mr. Qu.

163
00:07:46,923 --> 00:07:48,683
Do you think

164
00:07:49,003 --> 00:07:50,320
Shen Haoming

165
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:51,152
