174
00:08:23,363 --> 00:08:24,082
Use mine.

175
00:08:36,003 --> 00:08:36,682
Haochen.

176
00:08:37,363 --> 00:08:38,723
Grandma's cooking is delicious.

177
00:08:38,723 --> 00:08:39,483
