178
00:08:41,083 --> 00:08:41,682
Alright.

179
00:08:47,562 --> 00:08:48,162
Ignore me.

180
00:08:52,003 --> 00:08:52,922
Take a break.

181
00:08:58,363 --> 00:08:59,682
